message.body: Hey! Wie gehts!?!! I'm back from Berlin and am having a little gathering at my house tomorrow to celebrate my birthday. You around? It'll be early - say around 6:30-7:00 - as I need to work a double Beau on Sun. Would love to see you:-)
Hey glad to hear ur back, hope you had a good trip. Can't make it tomorrow as I will be 1 & half hours away for hunters opening in nj. We will have to meet up soon though.
